pedestrian, transmission of data, calculations and warning to make the driver/ pedestrian aware of dangerous situations to

avoid a collision, i.e. the system time available tsta, is determined by the speed of the car vcar, the deceleration acar of the car and the communication radius scom see (1). Without much loss of generality, the speed of the pedestrian is
assumed to be zero here.

